  "customContent": {
    "classFeatures": [
      {
        "index": "fighter-1-fighting-style",
        "name": "Fighting Style",
        "source": "PHB",
        "className": "Fighter",
        "level": 1,
        "desc": [
          "You adopt a particular style of fighting as your specialty. Choose one of the following options. You can't take the same Fighting Style option more than once, even if you get to choose again."
        ],
        "classIndex": "fighter",
        "gainedAtLevel": 1
      },
      {
        "index": "fighter-1-second-wind",
        "name": "Second Wind",
        "source": "PHB",
        "className": "Fighter",
        "level": 1,
        "desc": [
          "You have a limited well of stamina that you can draw on to protect yourself from harm. On your turn, you can use a bonus action to regain hit points equal to 1d10 + your fighter level. Once you use this feature, you must finish a short or long rest before you can use it again."
        ],
        "classIndex": "fighter",
        "gainedAtLevel": 1
      },
      {
        "index": "fighter-2-action-surge",
        "name": "Action Surge",
        "source": "PHB",
        "className": "Fighter",
        "level": 2,
        "desc": [
          "Starting at 2nd level, you can push yourself beyond your normal limits for a moment. On your turn, you can take one additional action. Once you use this feature, you must finish a short or long rest before you can use it again. Starting at 17th level, you can use it twice before a rest, but only once on the same turn."
        ],
        "classIndex": "fighter",
        "gainedAtLevel": 2
      },
      {
        "index": "fighter-3-martial-archetype",
        "name": "Martial Archetype",
        "source": "PHB",
        "className": "Fighter",
        "level": 3,
        "desc": [
          "At 3rd level, you choose an archetype from the list available that you strive to emulate in your combat styles and techniques. The archetype you choose grants you features at 3rd level and again at 7th, 10th, 15th, and 18th level."
        ],
        "classIndex": "fighter",
        "gainedAtLevel": 3
      }
    ],
